        <purpose>The Czech Vegetation Database aims to digitize all vegetation-plot records from the territory of the Czech Republic into a single database, facilitating easy access to relevant data for vegetation surveys, ecological analyses, and applications in nature conservation.</purpose>
        <gettingStarted><para>The detailed description of the data is available at:</para><para><ulink url="https://czechveg.github.io/Data/data_availability.html"><citetitle>https://czechveg.github.io/Data/data_availability.html</citetitle></ulink></para></gettingStarted>
        <acknowledgements><para>The list of data contributors and data managers is available on the website of the Czech Vegetation Database:</para><para><ulink url="https://czechveg.github.io/About/acknowledgements.html"><citetitle>https://czechveg.github.io/About/acknowledgements.html</citetitle></ulink></para></acknowledgements>
